                        fa.fa.fa-envelope.o
                        | &nbsp;Email us: hello@stayfavful.com
                    p
                        fa.fa.fa-map-marker
                        | &nbsp; Locate us: Sunway Nexis Soho, Kota Damansara, 1, Jalan PJU 5/1, Kota Damansara, 47810 




